attributes.value: Values independence

Values self-control

Values knowledge

Does not generally seek retribution for past wrongs
Is very rarely moved by curiosity
Shares intimate details of life without sparing a thought to repercussions or propriety
Does not generally respond to emotional appeals
Tries to keep her things orderly
Only rarely tries to assert herself in conversation
Likes a little excitement now and then
Strong
Almost never sick
A good intellect
